      "raw_text": "WASHINGTON, March 1.-THE senate committee on\nterritories today voted to report favorably the adms-\nsion of Arizona and New Mexico states. The vote\nstrictly party lines the republicans of the committee\nvoting favorably and the democrats opposing.\n\n\nThe bill gives each territory millions of acres with which\nto pay territorial bonds validated by acts of congress in\n1896"
